{"name":"Estimation","type":"trait","img":"icons/sundries/gaming/dice-runed-brown.webp","data":{"pointCost":2,"name":"","traittype":"die","text":"Dwarven Engineers often share with each other their vast knowledge. \"How far do y' think that is? \" \"Hunnert paces?\" \"Nah, hunnert seven and an eighth, easy.\" A Dwarf with this ability may add a +1D any skill that requires an estimation of distance, depth or height: building a bridge, carving out a hall or even leaping a chasm. Be warned though, estimating incorrectly can be calamitous. If the test is failed, the results are mismeasured to a castrophic or comical degree.\n\nRestrictions: Dwarves only","collapsed":true,"hasAptitudeModifier":false,"aptitudeModifier":0,"aptitudeTarget":"","hasDieModifier":false,"dieModifier":1,"dieModifierTarget":"","hasObModifier":false,"obModifierTarget":"All auditory-based Perception tests","obModifier":1,"addsReputation":false,"reputationName":"Bastard","reputationDice":1,"reputationInfamous":true,"addsAffiliation":false,"affiliationName":"","affiliationDice":0,"callonTarget":"","restrictions":"Dwarves only"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"TmE39BSdpoka2VQY":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_dgubyrm4iyo","path":"TRAITS#/CF_SEP/Dwarven Traits","color":"#000000"}},"_id":"qlphR42uGUxn337u"}
